libadwaita-1 (1.4.0-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Team upload
  * d/control: Stop generating from d/control.in
  * d/control: Build-depend on GIR XML included by Adw-1.gir.
    This will help with separating GIR XML out from -dev packages in
    future (Helps: #1030223)
  * d/control: Add ${gir:Provides}, ${gir:Depends} to -dev package
    (Helps: #1030223)
  * Don't build documentation unless building Architecture: all packages.
    This avoids redundantly building the documentation on every
    architecture's buildd: we only need to build it on the Architecture:
    all buildd, or when doing a combined any+all build.

